##Git For Beginners : Git Guide

Overview

Welcome to the Git Guide project! This multi-page website is designed to help new developers understand the basics of Git and GitHub. Whether you're just starting out or need a refresher, this guide will walk you through everything from creating a repository to managing branches and resolving merge conflicts.

This is a group project, and everyone has contributed to the creation of the website. Our main goal is to present Git concepts in a clear, practical way to help developers use version control in their daily workflows.

Table of Contents

Project Description

How to Use This Repository

